Ernest Hilliard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Hilliard 0 Ernest Hilliard (January 31, 1890 – September 3, 1947) was an American actor. He appeared in 98 films between 1921 and 1947. He was born in New York, New York and died in Santa Monica, California from a heart attack. Ernest_Hilliard ( January_31_,_1890 – September_3_,_1947 ) was an_American_actor .
